## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on publicly available information and may not cover all aspects of how scientific knowledge changes over time. The reliance on online platforms like Quora and Brainly may introduce biases, as these platforms include user-generated content that may not always be peer-reviewed or scientifically validated. Additionally, the dynamic nature of science means that new developments could quickly render some of the information outdated. Further research, including academic journal articles and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of this topic.

